        "action": "Award ESA for Life for Clin Depression which is Severe, Lifelong & Life-limiting",
        "additional_details": "I would like to see the law changed so that those who suffer unmanageable Clinical Depression like me are awarded ESA for life.\r\n",
        "background": "My name is Neville Bardoliwalla, I have been a lifelong sufferer of Clinical Depression plus also Acute Anxiety Disorder & Recurrent Symptoms of OCD. \r\n\r\nMy condition is considered Severe, lifelong and life-limiting, and I have been placed in the Support Group receiving ESA from the DWP.",
